text: Ed Levy (1916–2008) was a baseball player. Ed Levy or Ed Levi may also refer to: *Edward H. Levi (1911–2000), former United States Attorney General *Edward Lawrence Levy (1851–1932), British world weightlifting champion *Edward Lawrence Levy (fraudster) (died 1892), Victorian solicitor convicted of forgery, fraud and perjury *Ed Levy (tennis), tennis player (see SAP Open) *Ted Levy, rugby player *Edward Levy, horror writer *Edward Levy-Lawson, 1st Baron Burnham (1833–1916), British newspaper proprietor
title: Ed Levy (disambiguation)
